(373, 1, '2017-03-08 22:03:41', '2017-03-08 22:03:41', '[gallery link="none" ids="299,298,297"]\r\n\r\nAs We Know There Are Several Kinds Of Rats And Mice Such As "Hik Meeya, Uru Meeya, Kos Ata Meeya, etc ..". They Destroy Anything What They Found. Their Main Colonies Are Called "Mee Gula" Which Is Located Underground. Normally They Stealthily Come Out From Their Burrows At Night. Our Vision We Have A Separate Treatment For Different Type Of Rats By Combining Our Technical Know/How With The Experience Of Our Technical Staff, We Can Definitely Help You To Get Rid Of Your Problem About Rats. By Using Our Technical Knowledge And Our Experienced Technical Staff, We Can Easily Determine The Proper Palaces To Keep The Deadly Baits.', 'Rodent Control', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '58-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-08 22:03:41', '2017-03-08 22:03:41', '', 58, 'http://saran93.co.nf/2017/03/08/58-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
