(427, 1, '2017-03-11 23:00:23', '2017-03-11 23:00:23', '<strong><span style="color: #000000;">Started in 2006. Our company is based on vision of providing our prospecting clients a high quality professional service promptly and at reasonably competitive charges. By providing a client - friendly, cost - effective service covered with a guarantee, our aim in the long run is to win our clients confidence and good - will for the control benefit of both parties. Our endeavour is to help create an environmental free from pests enabling the people of our country enjoy a healthy life.</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #003366;"><strong>Our Vision </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>To protect our valued, prospective clients, in particular, and all Sri Lankan citizens, in general, from diverse problems arising due to pests, who cause various diseases and damage properties.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #003366;"><strong>Our Mission </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>To provide an effective, cost/effective and environment-friendly safe service to control pests by adapting methods of modern treatment and technology, to safeguard health and property of our valued clientele.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #003366;"><strong>Our Goal </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>To become the most reliable and recognized company in Sri Lanka in the sphere of pest control by applying highest standards of professionalism and using ultra - modern developments in technology to wipe out successfully the pest menace from the country.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000080;"><strong><span style="color: #003366;">Our Organization</span> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-339 size-full" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/img779.jpg" alt="" width="182" height="250" />\r\n<strong>Mr.Lalith Chaminda Wijewardena </strong>\r\n<strong>Proprietor - Dene Pest Control Services</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">We are a professional pest control organization with experience in th</span>is field. We adapt the most acceptable scientific approach to control pests such as rats, cockroaches, ants, flies, mosquitoes, termites, etc... safety is our main concern &amp; therefore we use only safe household pesticides, recommended by the register of pesticides in Sri Lanka. O</strong><strong>ur technical team is dedicated to control pests without polluting the environment and our company is backed by the most experienced technical staff in the pest control sphere in Sri Lanka. We are geared with up to date equipment and also competent enough to prepare specific pesticides to solve any pest control problem at a short notice. </strong><strong>Our services include the controlling of pests in hotels, restaurants, catering establishments, hospitals, factories, ware-houses, offices, residences, etc .., we undertake anti-termite soil treatment prior to construction of buildings and post-construction treatment to protect properly from the damage caused by termites(white-ants).</strong></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '42-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-11 23:00:23', '2017-03-11 23:00:23', '', 42, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/03/11/42-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
